 acct is gone, I can ask some things I didn't want to bring up before.  Well one thing comes to mind now.  Do you think there has been or still is hacking going on in EQ?  How can some people make ungodly amounts of platinum so fast at times?  I always thought there were hackers.  Perhaps they used some form of editing or maybe a hex program or some crap.<br>
<br>
Do any temp files actually get used on your system while you play then uploaded when you are done?  I don't see any other way a hacker could give him or herself plat otherwise.<br>
<br>
I know nobody would admit to it if there was but I always felt something was fishy at times with some of the people I knew. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><br>
